Overview

A web-based calculator that supports basic arithmetic operations with an interactive and responsive user interface.

Features

Basic Operations: Addition (+), Subtraction (-), Multiplication (*), Division (/)

Clear Button: Reset the input fields.

Error Handling: Prevent division by zero and invalid inputs.

Bonus Features:

Keyboard input support.

Calculation history (if enabled with a database).

Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS

Backend: Java (JSP & Servlets)

Database: MySQL (Optional - for storing history)

Version Control: GitHub
